snippet: Tens of thousands of Minnesota workers have raises coming after a new minimum wage law was signed Monday by Gov. Mark Dayton.
abstract: Minnesota Gov Mark Dayton signs new minimum wage law that will give raises to tens of thousands of workers in the state.
lead_paragraph: Tens of thousands of Minnesota workers have raises coming after a new minimum wage law was signed Monday by Gov. Mark Dayton.

headline.main: Minnesota: Governor Signs Into Law a Phased-In Rise in the Minimum Wage
headline.print_headline: Minnesota: Governor Signs Into Law a Phased-In Rise in the Minimum Wage
